{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/return-early-pattern-for-functions","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Obrazac Ranog Povratka iz Funkcije","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kada se naidje na <code>return</code> naredbu, izvrsavanje trenutne funkcije staje i kontrola se vraca mestu poziva.</p>\n<p><strong>Mfano</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">function myFun() {\n  console.log(\"Hello\");\n  return \"World\";\n  console.log(\"byebye\")\n}\nmyFun();\n</code></pre>\n<p>Ovo ce ispisati string <code>Hello</code> u konzoli i vratiti string <code>World</code>. String <code>byebye</code> nikada nece biti ispisan, jer funkcija izlazi na <code>return</code> naredbi.</p>\n</section>","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244c4","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Izmenite funkciju <code>abTest</code> tako da, ako je <code>a</code> ili <code>b</code> manje od <code>0</code>, funkcija odmah vrati <code>undefined</code>.</p>\n<p><strong>Podsetnik</strong>\nZapamtite da je <a href=\"https://www.freecodecamp.org/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/understanding-uninitialized-variables\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><code>undefined</code> kljucna rec</a>, a ne string.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18272,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/return-early-pattern-for-functions"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"// Setup\nfunction abTest(a, b) {\n  // Only change code below this line\n\n\n\n  // Only change code above this line\n\n  return Math.round(Math.pow(Math.sqrt(a) + Math.sqrt(b), 2));\n}\n\nabTest(2,2);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>abTest(2, 2)</code> treba da vrati broj</p>","testString":"assert(typeof abTest(2, 2) === 'number');"},{"text":"<p><code>abTest(2, 2)</code> treba da vrati <code>8</code></p>","testString":"assert(abTest(2, 2) === 8);"},{"text":"<p><code>abTest(-2, 2)</code> treba da vrati <code>undefined</code></p>","testString":"assert(abTest(-2, 2) === undefined);"},{"text":"<p><code>abTest(2, -2)</code> treba da vrati <code>undefined</code></p>","testString":"assert(abTest(2, -2) === undefined);"},{"text":"<p><code>abTest(2, 8)</code> treba da vrati <code>18</code></p>","testString":"assert(abTest(2, 8) === 18);"},{"text":"<p><code>abTest(3, 3)</code> treba da vrati <code>12</code></p>","testString":"assert(abTest(3, 3) === 12);"},{"text":"<p><code>abTest(0, 0)</code> treba da vrati <code>0</code></p>","testString":"assert(abTest(0, 0) === 0);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#basic-javascript","dashedName":"return-early-pattern-for-functions","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"basic-javascript","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/counting-cards","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/returning-boolean-values-from-functions","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244c4","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum) {\n  if (endNum - startNum === 0) {\n    return [startNum];\n  } else {\n    const numbers = rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum - 1);\n    numbers.push(endNum);\n    return numbers;\n  }\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/return-early-pattern-for-functions"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}